Key Match Events: Joey Veerman scored for Netherlands after only four minutes
Maximilian Mittelstädt scored for Germany seven minutes later
Niclas Füllkrug scored the winning goal for Germany in the 85th minute
Post-Match Reflections: Julian Nagelsmann praised the team's spirit and mix
Nagelsmann confirmed they can dominate matches and not just keep up with teams
The win gives Germany a big boost ahead of the Euro 2024 tournament
Miscellaneous Highlights: Germany had more than 70% possession in the first half
Donyell Malen and Memphis Depay came close for the Netherlands in the second half
Verbruggen made several important saves to keep the game competitive
